Name: We Have Come Into This Place G
ChorusText:
We have come into this place
(G)
We have come into this place
To gather
in His name
And worship Him
Worship Him, Jesus
Christ, our
Lord.
Let us lift up Holy hands
Magnify His name
And worship Him.
Worship Him, Jesus Christ
our
Lord.
So forget about yourselves
Concentrate on Him and worship Him
Worship Him, Jesus
Christ
our
Lord.
